  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Belvedere is an attractive hotel enjoying one of the most peaceful locations in <a data-udi="umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e163ac5c9114f0dae9f3f8d222fa730}" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, situated above the Lauterbrunnen Valley and just 5 minutes’ walk to the village centre and nearest ski lift.</p>
<p>This hotel overlooks the village and valley with a large sun terrace and veranda that captures the snowy mountain views. You’ll enjoy cuisine in the bright ‘Art Nouveau’ style dining room with large windows. Alternatively full paying guests receive a credit voucher of up to CHF 20 to dine à la carte at the Hotel Silberhorn, 8 minutes’ walk away. You can store your ski gear in the hotels heated boot room.</p>
<p>The bedrooms are bright and attractive, smaller rooms may have a sloping ceiling. South-facing rooms have valley views.</p>]]></description>
