  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Small Standard </strong>rooms are around 15<span>m² and some have a sloping ceiling. These rooms are north facing and sleep up to two adults.</span></p>
<p><strong>Standard </strong>twin rooms are around 20<span>m² and are north facing. These rooms can sleep up to four (with extra sofa bed or extra bunk beds).</span></p>
<p><strong>Jungfrau View</strong> rooms are around 20<span>m² and are south facing. These rooms can also sleep up to four (with extra sofa bed or extra bunk beds).</span></p>
<p><strong>Single</strong> rooms are around 12<span>m² and either north facing (standard) or south facing (Jungfrau View).</span></p>
<p><span>Many rooms interconnect, so please call us to request these.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
